<article id="post-29" class="post-29 page type-page status-publish hentry">
	<header class="entry-header"><h1 class="entry-title">Research Areas</h1></header><!-- .entry-header -->
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>The Institute of Safety/Security and Risk Sciences conducts interdisciplinary research, financed by federal funding and funding agencies (Third-party funds).</p>
<p>The Main Research areas are:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.risk.boku.ac.at/forschung/forschungsschwerpunkte/kernenergie/" >Nuclear Safety &amp; Security </a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.risk.boku.ac.at/forschung/forschungsschwerpunkte/erneuerbare-energie/" >Wind Energy</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.risk.boku.ac.at/forschung/forschungsschwerpunkte/risiko-und-technikfolgenforschung-im-bereich-bio-und-nanotechnologie/" >Risk and Technology Assessment of Bio- and Nanotechnology </a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.risk.boku.ac.at/forschung/forschungsschwerpunkte/technikfolgenabschatzung/" >Methodological Development of Prospective Technology Assessment</a></li>
</ul>
<p>Addtionally the ISR conducts in research in other areas, complementary to the main research areas.</p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->
</article><!-- #post-## -->

